AWS WAF  (Web Application Firewall)
    
    A web application firewall that helps to protect your web apps from common web exploits
    Wokrs at layer 7 of the OSI model designed to stop attackers from doing cross site scripting or sql injections

AWS Shield
    
    AWS Shield is a managed DDOS protection service that safeguards web applications running on AWS 

    Provides always-on detection and automatic inline mitigations
    Has two tiers standard and advanced(3000 a month for advanced)
